{"ts": "2026-06-08T23:50:47.657465+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Based on my analysis of the repository, here's what I found:\n\n## Runtime Profiles Documented\n\nThe template defines **5 runtime profiles** in the README:\n\n1. **local** - Development environment that works even without network connection\n2. **local-dev** - Connects to DEV environment from local machine\n3. **dev** - For deploying Development environments\n4. **staging** - For deploying Staging environments\n5. **live** - For deploying Live environments\n\n## Recommended Developer Setup\n\n### Git Hook for Linting\n```bash\ngit config core.hookspath .githooks\n```\nThis enables the pre-commit hook that runs `./gradlew checkFormat` on every commit, using the **Spring Java Format** plugin (v0.0.47) with space indentation.\n\n### IntelliJ IDEA Configuration\nFor easier test execution:\n- Navigate to: **Build, Execution, Deployment > Build Tools > Gradle > Run tests using > IntelliJ IDEA**\n- For Spring Java Format integration in IDEA, follow the [Spring Java Format IntelliJ IDEA guide](https://github.com/spring-io/spring-javaformat#intellij-idea)\n\n### Test Tasks Available\n- **`test`** - Main CI task (excludes 'develop' and 'restdocs' tags)\n- **`unitTest`** - Fast, isolated tests (excludes 'develop', 'context', 'restdocs')\n- **`contextTest`** - Integration tests with SpringContext (includes 'context')\n- **`restDocsTest`** - Tests for generating API documentation (includes 'restdocs')\n- **`developTest`** - Tests not meant for CI, good for learning (includes 'develop')\n\n### Linting\n- Uses `io.spring.javaformat` plugin applied to all subprojects via `lint.gradle`\n- `checkFormat` task validates code formatting\n- Configuration: `.springjavaformatconfig` (space indentation)", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 940, "prompt_tokens": 8107, "total_tokens": 9047, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 537, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 7488, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0011140218, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0002962218, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.0008178}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780962629-pbyHERgzerwHPBHorW7f", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea9a5-173c-72e1-bcae-638177b93945-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 8107, "output_tokens": 940, "total_tokens": 9047, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 7488}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 537}}}}]}}}
